{"tid":1709322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"是日文宣大方向！","createTime":"2019-11-12T00:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T11:53:23.000Z","uid":42392,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f26d3e6cc38d5d786aab04550618d6950f51dd61","tid":1709322,"uid":42392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T00:49:43.000Z","msg":"今朝搭鐵返工嘅時候 太多人想上車搞到閂唔到門<br />\n<br />\n之後就有啲帶住小朋友嘅師奶屌 點解阻佢地返學考試  小朋友係無辜架 佢地仲未到要承受依啲野嘅年紀<br />\n<br />\n佢話自己都係黃 都好憎啲死黑警 但個小朋友冇得返學考試 可能咁就一世<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能我地一路以黎嘅文宣太過同溫層 正係關注係警暴等方面，雖然佢地都收到曬  <br />\n但仲未令一啲淺黃佢地明白到 依加要犧牲同放棄一啲野嘅重要性<br />\n<br />\n做法上可能冇乜太大改善空間 但係文宣可以做返足啲 e.g解釋返點解要阻人返工 <br />\n今日好多人係車上互屌 明明大家都係同路人 但依樣野好大可能會分化到我地 同一班淺黃"},{"pid":"3c6604a28b086e467d943ecb55c292bba237dd15","tid":1709322,"uid":42392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:39:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"331cde68586fea79f20f970bc321ecd82ff6aef2","tid":1709322,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50705668a7389794db239d7993ae1c0d431ad93b","tid":1709322,"uid":42392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:56:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4379b374dd9a3cfaa43139111a169787a6d456ca","tid":1709322,"uid":87582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:59:06.000Z","msg":"未叫未承受到？<br />\n20幾歲承受到比政權逼害？要食真彈？<br />\n你係依個社會嘅持分者<br />\n有啲野唔係你主動要做<br />\n但你係有責任可承擔"},{"pid":"cf0836fe66331abeb387ccc54783d27c9eb3a8b8","tid":1709322,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa5c7c1a95425ff77cab49a4367f88b917bc8de","tid":1709322,"uid":338632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor